    <section class="services-blog">

      <div class="services-blog__item">
          <div class="item__text">
            <h2>Trucking</h2>

            <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" provides services for the transportation of goods by the following types of road transport: </p>

            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>Tent trucks</li>
              <li>Open side cars</li>
              <li>Container trucks</li>
              <li>Tank trucks</li>
              <li>Tanker trucks</li>
              <li>Platforms and low-frame trawls</li>
              <li>Isothermal cars</li>
              <li>Refrigerated cars</li>
              <li>Timber trucks</li>
              <li>Сar transporters</li>
            </ul>

            <p>We carry out transportation of goods by road in the following areas:</p>

            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>Cargo transportation in Russia</li>
              <li>The countries of the Eurasian Economic Union (Kazakhstan, Belarus, Armenia, Kyrgyzstan)</li>
              <li>The countries of Asia (China, Mongolia, Georgia, Tajikistan, Uzbekistan)</li>
              <li>Baltic Countries (Lithuania, Latvia, Estonia)</li>
              <li>European Union countries (Germany, Austria, Czech Republic and others)</li>
            </ul>

            <p>In addition, we have the possibility of customs clearance and insurance of all cargo.</p>
          </div>

        <img src="../http://images.trans-s.su/assets/images/autogruz.jpg"  class="pull-right">
      </div>

      <div class="services-blog__item">
        <div class="item__text">

          <h2>Rail freight</h2>

          <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" renders services in cargo transportation by the following types of rolling stock:</p> 

          <ul class="text__list">
            <li>Platforms</li>
            <li>Gondola cars</li>
            <li>Covered wagons</li>
            <li>Tanks</li>
            <li>Transporters</li>
          </ul>

           <p>We carry out transportation of goods by rail in the following areas:</p>

          <ul class="text__list">
            <li>Cargo transportation in Russia</li>
            <li>The countries of the Eurasian Economic Union (Kazakhstan, Belarus, Armenia, Kyrgyzstan)</li>
            <li>The countries of Asia (China, Mongolia, Georgia, Tajikistan, Uzbekistan)</li>
            <li>Baltic Countries (Lithuania, Latvia, Estonia)</li>
            <li>European Union countries (Germany, Austria, Czech Republic and others)</li>
          </ul>

           <p>In addition, we have the possibility of customs clearance and insurance of all cargo.</p>
        </div>

        <img src="../http://images.trans-s.su/assets/images/zheleznodorog.jpg"  class="pull-right">
      </div>

      <div class="services-blog__item">
        <div class="item__text">
            <h2>Marine cargo transportation</h2>

            <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" provides a full range of services related to the carriage of goods by sea, including: </p>

            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>Selection of the optimal logistic scheme</li>
              <li>Chartering of vessels</li>
              <li>Cargo delivery to ports</li>
              <li>Cargo tracking</li>
              <li>Execution of a full package of documents</li>
            </ul>

             <p>We carry out transportation of goods by sea in the following directions:</p>

            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>The countries of Asia</li>
              <li>The countries of Europe</li>
              <li>The countries of Africa</li>
              <li>The countries of&nbsp;America</li>
              <li>The countries of Australia</li>
            </ul>

             <p>In addition, we have the possibility of customs clearance and insurance of all cargo.</p>
          </div>
          
          <img src="../http://images.trans-s.su/assets/images/more.jpg"  class="pull-right">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-blog__item">

        <div class="item__text">
          <h2>Multimodal cargo transportation</h2>

            <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" renders a full complex of services connected with multimodal transportation of cargoes by automobile, railway and sea transport, including: </p>

          <ul class="text__list">
            <li>Selection of the optimal logistic scheme</li>
            <li>Chartering of ships, delivery of goods to ports</li>
            <li>Delivery of goods to railway platforms</li>
            <li>Organization of loading when changing the mode of transport</li>
            <li>Organization of temporary storage</li>
            <li>Cargo tracking</li>
            <li>Execution of a full package of documents</li>
          </ul>

           <p>We carry out multimodal transportation of cargoes in the following directions:</p>

          <ul class="text__list">
            <li>The countries of Asia</li>
            <li>The countries of Europe</li>
            <li>The countries of Africa</li>
            <li>The countries of America</li>
            <li>The countries of Australia</li>
          </ul>

           <p>In addition, we have the possibility of customs clearance and insurance of all cargo.</p>
        </div>
        
        <img src="../http://images.trans-s.su/assets/images/multi2.jpg"  class="pull-right">
      </div>

      <div class="services-blog__item">

          <div class="item__text">
            <h2>Oversized cargo transportation</h2>

            <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" renders services in transportation of oversized cargoes by the following types of transport:</p> 
            
            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>Automobile transport</li>
              <li>Railway transport</li>
              <li>Sea transport</li>
            </ul>


            <p>We carry out transportation of oversized cargo in the following areas:</p>

            <ul class="text__list">
              <li>Cargo transportation in Russia</li>
              <li>The countries of the Eurasian Economic Union (Kazakhstan, Belarus, Armenia, Kyrgyzstan)</li>
              <li>The countries of Asia</li>
              <li>The countries of Europe</li>
              <li>The countries of Africa</li>
              <li>The countries of America</li>
              <li>The countries of Australia</li>
            </ul>

            <p>In addition, we have the possibility of customs clearance and insurance of all cargo.</p>
          </div>
        
        <img src="../http://images.trans-s.su/assets/images/negabaritnyiy-gruz.jpg"  class="pull-right">
      </div>

      <div class="services-blog__item">

        <div class="item__text">
          <h2>Customs clearance</h2>

          <p>The company "TRANSSERVICE" renders services in the organization of customs clearance when moving goods across the customs border of the Russian Federation by road, rail or sea, including: </p>

          <ul class="text__list">
            <li>Preparation of a package of documents for the declaration of goods</li>
            <li>Electronic declaration of goods under EXPORT from the territory of the Russian Federation</li>
